Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 01 of Spine MRI
When I select 'Spine' radio button
Then multiple choice Localizer is enabled

When I click on the Localizer
Then a Localizer canvas pops up

When I select C0
Then C0 is selected and turns red
When I select C7
Then C7 is selected and turns red
And C1, C2, C3, C4, C5 and C6 are automatically selected and turns red

When I click on X on the top right corner
Then the canvas is closed
